<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>
		<title>
			{% block title %}U-PARTENAIRE | Authentification
			{% endblock %}
		</title>
		<link
		rel="shortcut icon" href="{{asset('dist/img/upharma.png')}}"/>
		<!-- Google Font: Source Sans Pro -->
		<link
		rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro:300,400,400i,700&display=fallback">
		<!-- Font Awesome -->
		<link
		rel="stylesheet" href="{{asset('plugins/fontawesome-free/css/all.min.css')}}">
		<!-- icheck bootstrap -->
		<link
		href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
		<!-- Theme style -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{asset('dist/css/login.css')}}">
		{% block stylesheets %}
			{# {{ encore_entry_link_tags('app') }} #}
		{% endblock %}


	</head>
	<body class="gray-bg">

		<div class="loginColumns animated fadeInDown">
			<div class="row" style="margin-right: -15px !important;margin-left: -15px !important;">

				<div class="col-md-6"><br><br><br><br><br>
					<h2 class="font-bold">UPHARMA</h2>
					<div style="color:#949494;font-size:14px !important">
						<p style="color:#949494;font-size:14px !important">
							UPHARMA est un progiciel de gestion intégré (PGI, ERP en anglais)  développé pour les petites et moyennes entreprises, les indépendants, auto-entrepreneurs ou les associations.
						</p>

						<p style="color:#949494;font-size:14px !important">
							À savoir la gestion des clients, fournisseurs, devis, commandes, factures, stocks, comptabilité. L’architecture d’UPHARMA  est modulaire. Il se positionne sur la facilité d'installation et la simplicité d'utilisation.
						</p>

						<p style="color:#949494;font-size:14px !important">
							UPHARMA  fonctionne par activation de modules. Vous n'activez et ne voyez que les fonctionnalités (modules) dont vous avez besoin.
						</p>
					</div>

				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="test row">
						<div class="col-1"></div>

						<div class="col-12">
							<centre>

								<img src="/dist/img/upharma.png" alt="image" class="feed-photo" style="width: 25%; margin-left: 16%;">
								<span style="vertical-align: middle; font-family: Oswald,sans-serif;font-size: 40px;font-weight: bold;color: #CDDFF2;">
									UPHARMA
								</span>

							</center>

						</div>


					</div>
					<div class="test row">

						<div class="col-12">
							<img src="/dist/img/universal.PNG" alt="image" class="feed-photo" style="width: 80%; margin-left: 10%;">
						</div>

					</div>
					<div class="ibox-content">


						<form method="post" style="padding:10px">
							{% if error %}
								<div class="login__error">{{ error.messageKey|trans(error.messageData, 'security') }}</div>
							{% endif %}

							<div class="form-group">
								<input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Username" value="{{ last_username }}" name="username" id="inputUsername" autocomplete="username" required autofocus style="padding:6px;margin-bottom:10px">
							</div>

							<div class="form-group">
								<input type="password" class="form-control" name="password" placeholder="Mots de pass" id="inputPassword" required style="padding:6px">
							</div>
							<br/>
							<input type="hidden" name="_csrf_token" value="{{ csrf_token('authenticate') }}">


							<button class="btn btn-primary block full-width m-b" type="submit">
								Connexion
							</button>
						</form>

					</div>
				</div>

			</div><hr/>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-6" style="
																														    font-size: 11px;
																														">
					Universal , scientific system & software
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6 text-right">
					<small>© 2024</small>
				</div>
			</div>

		</body>
		<!-- jQuery -->
		<script src="{{asset('plugins/jquery/jquery.min.js')}}"></script>
		<!-- Bootstrap 4 -->
		<script src="{{asset('plugins/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')}}"></script>
		<!-- AdminLTE App -->
		<scrip src="{{asset('dist/js/adminlte.min.js')}}"></script>
		<scrip src="{{asset('dist/js/components/login/login.js')}}"></script>
	</body>
</html>
